<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content container">
    <p class="hero-catchphrase">仕事帰りに、安心の医療を。</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      <span class="hero-title-main">勾当台夕方内科クリニック</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-description">
      水曜〜日曜、17:00〜21:00まで診療<br />
      勾当台公園駅から徒歩2分
    </p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="badge">夕方専門診療</span>
      <span class="badge">土日も診療</span>
      <span class="badge">駅チカ</span>
    </div>
    <a href="#reservation" class="hero-cta">ご予約・お問い合わせ</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 70px;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      #e8f4f8 0%,
      #d4e8ef 50%,
      #c5dce6 100%
    );
    z-index: -2;
  }

  .hero-bg::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -30%;
    width: 80%;
    height: 150%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      rgba(74, 144, 164, 0.15) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
  }

  .hero-bg::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20%;
    left: -20%;
    width: 60%;
    height: 80%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      rgba(107, 179, 201, 0.1) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-catchphrase {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4a90a4;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .hero-title {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-title-main {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2c5f7c;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .hero-badges {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #4a90a4;
    color: #4a90a4;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 50px;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90a4, #3d7a8c);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(74, 144, 164, 0.4);
    transition:
      transform 0.2s,
      box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(74, 144, 164, 0.5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 20px);
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
    }

    .hero-catchphrase {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .hero-title-main {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 6px 16px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      padding: 14px 36px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>
